          "Logan Boese"
        ],
        [
          "Staff Generated History"
        ],
        [
          "You were always a watchful sort. Grew up in the middle of the country, raised as a proud patriot. Went to high school and graduated with Honours. Went almost immediately into the military. The track you were on lead you through all manner of boot camps and training. Before at last you ended up a marksman in a Specialised Branch that saw you deployed to some of the darkest situations anyone in this generation has ever seen. You were part of a unit deployed with the expectation that when you went, everything in the immediate vicinity was to be as good as dead. You went career, and saw more than your fair share of humanity's worst, before you couldn't take it anymore, and took retirement as early as possible. When you got out, you went off the grid, and started using your survival training to live off the land. At least, that was, until you were approached for a \"Special Mission\" by a man with a shiny set of butter bars you'd never seen or heard of before. He made it clear that it was not up for debate, and if you didn't go, you'd end up detained or worse. You were deployed, using the term loosely, to eliminate a target in the city. And you did it. Efficiently. Efficiently enough that when you were debriefed, the man who'd \"hired\" you revealed a pair of fangs and had his subordinates bring you into the fold. Since then you've been briefed on your new situation, and released into the wild with the expectation of awaiting your next deployment. With your new condition, though you were more at home in the wilderness, that's near suicide for you now, and it's safer to be among your own kind. You're given to understand that with your new targets, bows and arrows, while conspicuous, are very effective methods of neutralizing threats. You're a survivor, and you can make the best of almost any situation you find yourself in. This is just one more mission, and it's one you're planning to dominate."
        ],
        [
          "Sire:",
          "Liam Piney",
          "Reference: (If any)",
          "",
          "",
          "Clan",
          "Caitiff - Weak Blood"
        ],
